{"tid":1067976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中綫重驗鋼筋  首批樣本38%不合格","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T04:01:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0006ad4d8c445fe130a5a0f38498b075626b8a00","tid":1067976,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190319/20636356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F20636356&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKnHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=f7c358ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F20636356&h=2b034d8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190319/20636356</a><br />\n<br />\n沙中綫重驗鋼筋 <br />\n首批樣本38%不合格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190319/large/18748968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F18748968.jpg&h=cf93ea4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵上周重啟沙中綫紅磡站月台層板的超聲波檢驗。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵上周重啟沙中綫紅磡站月台層板的超聲波檢驗後，路政署昨公佈重檢後首批21支鋼筋接駁樣本結果，有八支扭入長度低於政府要求，最嚴重只扭入9.5毫米，被列為不合格，總計不合格率38%；另有五支早前檢測被列為不合格，重檢後變合格，兩次檢測誤差高達7.8毫米。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵去年底以超音波檢測法量度鋼筋扭入螺絲帽長度，後被揭誤差極大而叫停。政府上周接納港鐵修正方案，檢測工作隨即恢復，早前檢測過的百多支樣本亦重驗。<br />\n<br />\n昨公佈的21支鋼筋樣本檢測結果，有10支扭入螺絲帽長度高於37毫米的政府要求，列為合格；有8支扭入長度介乎9.5毫米至36.4毫米，列為不合格；另三支樣本列為「未能提供可靠結果」，但署方未有解釋原因。統計重啟後結果，不合格率約38%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190319/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190319%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=13a6f925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五樣本不合格變合格<br />\n<br />\n是次公佈大部份均是重驗結果，比較兩次檢測，有五支樣本早前被列為不合格，是次重驗卻變成合格。其中一支位於東西走廊香港體育館區連續牆頂樣本，早前檢測只扭入36.65毫米，重檢卻為44.5豪米；誤差最大是東西走廊B區連續牆底樣本，早前量度到34.8毫米，重檢後為42.3毫米，誤差高達7.8毫米。<br />\n<br />\n路政署亦披露八支沒接駁螺絲帽鋼筋資料，有5支絞牙僅0至4圈扭紋，有被剪短之嫌（正常鋼筋絞牙有11圈扭紋）；另亦在層板內發現三個非原設計一部份的螺絲帽。<br />\n■記者梁御和  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n涉擲物施襲威脅燒屋  包致金姪女 嫌母愛不夠<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n泳線牟利 泳總自己查自己"},{"pid":"8cc3d672cb113c7f83ea6ffe19f9dd83574f0798","tid":1067976,"uid":2521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"睇黎要再改改個測試方法同要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a81a0aee2f293578e373b2f44955df504d715ba","tid":1067976,"uid":208251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"重新起過又點話，時享un un腳攞多筆錢繼續fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832b031eebc12a97ef30d88d9960b3fa7c96b693","tid":1067976,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"新嘅測試方式不合格"},{"pid":"99d85287955bd62b62a50d98532b7ddea3af8587","tid":1067976,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"想改檢驗方法改到合格為止？"},{"pid":"dca8c0586408fcf8b1ab6e3e89ad9584a7cea944","tid":1067976,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"驗1000次 驗到合格為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74871bb9b8566300a451172ee488b7c37a5321b","tid":1067976,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"再改下啦，改到90%合格，收貨，通車"},{"pid":"4d5da73499d0f395b9349be1047133d9d1cffaf3","tid":1067976,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果喺呢個站發生嚴重追撞, 會唔會成個站倒塌"},{"pid":"6822a48a9fac122bef25550018c62ae71cc961a5","tid":1067976,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d5da73499d0f395b9349be1047133d9d1cffaf3","t